data.description: This property combines the charm of rural Idaho living with the luxury and comfort of a spacious 3716 square ft, 7-bedroom home, with an option for an office and bonus room. It's a wine-enthusiast dream, with a great patio, custom fire pit and seating to enjoy your own private vineyard. Your very own personal vineyard adds a unique touch, making it an ideal property for those who appreciate both the beauty of the outdoors and the possibility of making your own wine. Includes a three car garage with a 80 gallon, 5 horsepower compressor with three conveniently situated ports with reels. This property has investment opportunity for the short term rental market, if you choose. Each room is set up with private code entrance and automated lights. Please inquire previous earnings. This house has the ability to pay itself off while you live in it.
